               <p>He was a second time indicted for <rs id="t17261012-38-off156" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17261012-38-off156" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17261012-38-off156" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
               assaulting Sarah the <rs id="t17261012-38-viclabel157" type="occupation">Wife</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17261012-38-victim257 t17261012-38-viclabel157"></join> of 
                     <persName id="t17261012-38-victim245" type="victimName">
                        Robert 
                        king 
