               <p>He was a third time indicted for <rs id="t17261012-38-off158" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17261012-38-off158" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17261012-38-off158" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
